node.text: Never ever thought I would be able to buy what me and @jannid just bought! The most amazing piece of land in Stockholms archiapelago just 20 mins from the city center where we will spend the next couple years building our dream summer home! A picture just does not do it justice so just hit the link in my bio if you are curious of the full property video tour! ❤️❤️❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jon Olsson Delér on June 27, 2021 tagging @jannid, and @cestnormal. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and footwear.

node.text: A few years ago I thought that doing a couple hoodies and T shirts as Vlog mercendice would be a good plan. That quickly turned into something more and @cestnormal was born and here we are a couple years later digging into complex fabric composition, finetuning specsheets for every size of every item, shooting 3600 photos for the website and sorting 25 000 items for this drop at the warehouse( that has to be enough to not sell out in 2 minutes! 😅). So the little merchendice idea has quickly escalated into a full blown clothing brand going far beyond a standard T shirt with a print on. I love every part of it but the part I like the most is the fact that we truly have a tiny tiny team so I get to work with every aspect of the company from zipper quality all the way to setting up the studio lights to shoot the collection! ❤️ The website just opened up for preview for the upcoming launch tomorrow at 19.00 CET so if you are curious just go have a look! Could not be more proud of what our tiny team has been able to achive! ❤️

node.text: Back by insanely popular demand. Excited to fully release the collab with @towelclub. This brand only makes clothing in terry cloth fabric and these towel suits we’ve developed together is an absolute bathrobe killer. We will be living in this all summer. Perfect for post swim/surf/shower/kite, on the boat and also just to lounge in whenever. Has a zipper in the crotch so works as a poncho as well. Get yours before it's gone! (Leon also wanted me to tell you to spam @towelclub and tell them to make more products for kids as his outfit is only a sample!) 😅#linkinbio

Photo by Jon Olsson Delér in Marbella, Spain with @wflworldrun. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Today @wflworldrun is happening which is one of the events I value most during the whole year! It’s important to me as it’s a charity race where all proceeds go to spinal cord injury research. This year I have really prepared for it by running 120-150km/month with the goal of being able to run 30km so I am more than bummed out that I am laying in bed sick and can’t join the race and run side by side with my friends! (Covid test was negative though so that’s at least good) But since I can’t be out running to support this great cause I will be donating 10 000€ to the foundation as it’s something very close to my heart after having seen friends sustain spinal cord injuries! So I hope everyone who ran had an amazing time and I will continue to train to be able to reach higher goals and keep bringing avareness to this great cause next year! ❤️
